--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Name   : mariadb
Type   : Ansible role

Authors: liv community
License: Simplified BSD License

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
DESCRIPTION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

MariaDB is a multi-user, multi-threaded SQL database server. It is a
client/server implementation consisting of a server daemon (mysqld) and many
different client programs and libraries. This package contains the MariaDB
server and some accompanying files and directories. MariaDB is a community
developed branch of MySQL.

For more detailed information on the usage and available configuration options
please consult the following sections.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
USAGE
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

INSTALL
  - hosts: all
    roles:
      - role: mariadb
    vars:
      mariadb_state: 'install'

ENABLE
  - hosts: all
    roles:
      - role: mariadb
    vars:
      mariadb_state: 'enable'

DISABLE
  - hosts: all
    roles:
      - role: mariadb
    vars:
      mariadb_state: 'disable'

REMOVE
  - hosts: all
    roles:
      - role: mariadb
    vars:
      mariadb_state: 'remove'

INACTIVE
  - hosts: all
    roles:
      - role: mariadb
    vars:
      mariadb_state: 'inactive'

